{"tid":1749962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下一步 不消費聖誕","createTime":"2019-11-24T07:54:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T08:48:31.000Z","uid":42246,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8ed2b3af90a2ddd4f9f9fcbd507998768d30f2b7","tid":1749962,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:54:47.000Z","msg":"政府想12月25前回歸平靜 食聖誕同新年生意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年目標<br />\n不消費/只消費黃店聖誕<br />\n<br />\n今年香港搞成咁 有人死有人傷 根本唔值得慶祝<br />\n唔買禮物/DIY禮物 <br />\n唔出去食飯/食黃店/返屋企煮<br />\n<br />\n食完出去睇燈飾 嗌口號<br />\n<br />\n點都唔會比政府好過 <br />\n我睇攬炒你個聖誕 政府頂到幾撚耐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一句講曬 真香港人唔會有心情慶祝今年聖誕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍店全部去IFC啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80cddbe4f6346d119323c68fe8b0e66e5818e53","tid":1749962,"uid":126371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:57:03.000Z","msg":"#又一城"},{"pid":"a1e5e2d6513d674ab1a622692f4d443a22913d10","tid":1749962,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:57:35.000Z","msg":"當然有五大訴求就另計啦<br />\n<br />\n但冇就 1蚊都唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ee58577af9fdb8213083aa60cf858d527e3ea9","tid":1749962,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a80cddbe4f6346d119323c68fe8b0e66e5818e53","tid":1749962,"uid":126371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:57:03.000Z","msg":"#又一城"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:57:46.000Z","msg":"依個開都開唔返"},{"pid":"da0eb4eed8a695a3933b9ed67969d06b0a7b5364","tid":1749962,"uid":234658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T07:59: